data.description: Incredible opportunity to own a well-maintained, one-level home just minutes from downtown Thayne - with no current active HOA. This one-owner, inviting home offers an open kitchen/living concept, three bedrooms, two bathrooms and a nice yard with some improvements such as gravel pathway/driveway with plentiful room to park all the toys! Beautiful finishes throughout, including hardwood floors, granite, tile, solid wood doors and trim and alder kitchen cabinets. A must see!
